Package logic

Class User

java.lang.Object
logic.User
Direct Known Subclasses:
Costumer, Worker
public class User extends Object
The User class represents a user with various attributes such as user ID, ID number, name, password, contact information and user type. It also includes methods to get and set the values of these attributes as well as a toString method to print the user's information.
Author:
Mahran
